This paper deals with the problem of self-driving cars, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper proposes a method for transferring semantic information to unseen weather conditions, which involves training a perception module using semantic labels (cs.CV). The paper also uses a generative adversarial network (GAN) for unsupervised learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of vehicle control, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.SY.
